# Stopwatch Project

## Overview

This project is a simple Stopwatch implemented using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It provides users with features to measure elapsed time in hours, minutes, seconds, and milliseconds.

## Features

- Start, stop, and reset functionality
- Accurate measurement including milliseconds
- Responsive design
- Implemented with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript
- Easy to integrate and customize

